</div>
<p>Hello Meeta</p>
<p>I made these today as first day Ganpati prasad. They were a massive hit. An old lady I met said she had been coming to the temple for 8 years and this is the first time she’s had modaks this delicious and gorgeous looking (I did the traditional hand pleating of the covering)</p>
<p>Another lady asked if I take orders. </p>
<p>I just smiled and gave them the links to your recipe. </p>
<p>Getting all the appreciation made my day. Hope reading about it makes yours too! </p>
<p>Ganpati bappa morya!</p>
